  "body": "As per our discussion on 08/02/19 with @JonathanLorimer @wemeetagain @GregTheGreek @ansermino\r\n\r\nWe have decided to temporarily take focus off of [fixed-size-number-ts](www.github.com/chainsafesystems/fixed-sized-number-ts) and explore using big numbers.\r\n\r\nWe could utilize javascript `number` api for everything under `2**53 - 1` (i.e uint8, uint16, ....).\r\n\r\nAny notes I missed please add them.",
